title: The Carrie Diaries

genres: Amy B Harris, Candace Bushnell, Josh Schwartz, Len Goldstein, Miguel Arteta, Stephanie Savage

description: Satirical take on news events, celebrities, sports and the world of entertainment.
genres: Will Graham, Julie Smith, Jim Biederman

title: Star Wars: The Clone Wars
description: Yoda, Anakin and the Jedi Knights fight in the Clone Wars, taking them to many new planets and introducing new players. The series spans the time between 'Star Wars Episode II: Attack of the Clones' and 'Star Wars Episode III: Revenge of the Sith.'

title: Star Wars Rebels
description: A group of rebels try to stop the Empire from spreading tyranny throughout the galaxy.

title: Star Wars: Clone Wars---'The Epic Micro Series'
description: Animation featuring Anakin Skywalker and the Jedi Knights against the Separatists led by Count Dooku. This `micro series' picks up where the feature film `Star Wars Episode II: Attack of the Clones' left off.

title: Coming Home
description: Unexpected reunions between military personnel and their families are chronicled.

title: Ancient Aliens
description: A series exploring theories regarding supposed alien visitations involving ancient civilizations.

title: MTV 10 on Top
description: A countdown of the most talked-about celebrities of the week.

title: The 100
description: Juvenile prisoners from a space-station society are exiled to Earth decades after the planet was destroyed by nuclear war.
genres: Bharat Nalluri, Gina Girolamo, Jason Rothenberg, Leslie Morgenstein, Matt Miller

title: Room 101
description: Celebrities compete to get their pet hates put into Room 101.

title: Arthur
description: Popular animated series about a young aardvark, his family and friends. Based on the books by Marc Brown.
